* TESTING
** Create a manpage to use as a test spec.
Manpages are created in markdown (.ronn) files and converted to roff
with the ronn(1) command (app-text/rong-ng) in Gentoo Linux.
[1] dblookup.1
[2] mkdb.1 (a symlink to the above)

** Create test cases for the use cases in the manpage.


